fields.name: WOD1
fields.description:
Squat Clean
Build to a 1RM

Front Squat
Heavy Double

“Tiger Blood”
3 Rounds:
10 Clean and Jerks (135/95)
400 Meter Run

Gymnastics Conditioning
Not For Time:
5 Giant Sets:
3-5 Parallette Handstand Push-ups 
7 Strict Chest to Bar Pull-ups 
9 Strict Toes to Bar 
Rest 2-3 Minutes Between Sets.
